Output assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

Env REPASO_DATA_FILE /home/pencho/Development/repaso-tracker/demo_data.json

Hide
Type "cd ~/Development/repaso-tracker"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 1s
Type "repaso"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 1s
Type "repaso list"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 1s
Type "repaso stats"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
